# Templates

- **`templates/index.template.html`** is the main SPA shell (very large). Search before editing; avoid unrelated churn.
- **Configuration modal:** sidebar tabs (Settings, Subject Configuration, Custom Voices, etc.); **Settings** tab includes **Chat Settings** and **Voice and Image Settings** (`#message-font-size`, `#show-audio-tags`, `#auto-open-suggestions`, user LLM keys section, …). New checkboxes there need matching **`DOM`** + **`Config`** entries in `foundation.js` if they persist locally.
- New UI: prefer reusing existing modal/button classes (`modal-btn`, `modal-btn-primary`, etc.) and patterns from nearby sections.
- New deferred scripts: place after `app.js` and follow `CLAUDE.md` / frontend rule for init order.
